text: 97.5 Radyo Komunidad is an FM radio station owned by the National Nutrition Council under the Nutriskwela Community Radio Network in partnership with the City Government of Isabela and the United Evangelical Church of Isabela - Volunteer Firefighter and Rescue Group. Its studios and transmitter are located at the 3rd floor, Tan Building, Valderosa St., Isabela, Basilan.Nutriskwela Radyo KomunidadBasilan radio anchors tackle gender- sensitive reporting ==References== Category:Radio stations established in 2011 Category:Radio stations in Zamboanga City
